    "body": "Currently, we do some thread local caching of buffers in order to reduce buffer copying when using the typical `XContentFactory#jsonBuilder` (for example). This can create dangerous bugs of overlapping buffers if the builder is not passed to the API right when its created. Remove this behavior, and optimize in other manners in order to reduce buffer copying.\n\nNote, this means that the \"safe\" methods will be removed from the `XContentFactory`.\n", 
